{"tid":1306452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無槍無炮 點革命？","createTime":"2019-07-11T07:02:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T07:03:43.000Z","uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c5dc2dd7a9b98c9f3735e3eeabab1bbde8b27a3f","tid":1306452,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T07:02:36.000Z","msg":"我夠膽講，就算個個有槍有炮，咪又係都唔會用！<br />\n<br />\n因為大家想行動升級，但心態上仲未升級。<br />\n<br />\n想講既係心態重要過有無槍有無炮。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打不還手？ok <br />\n<br />\n但明顯經歷左612, 76, 77，<br />\n<br />\n和平賺民意一早做左幾次， <br />\n <br />\n我地煲大佢，指出<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">是你教我打不還手無用</span>既道理。<br />\n<br />\n唔係鼓吹暴力，但最少心態上要知道唔可以再loop 2014<br />\n<br />\n雨傘打不還手既軟弱心態，最後大家終日活係無力同恐懼，<br />\n<br />\n最後又變做更加順既順民。<br />\n<br />\n最低限度，好似見到非禮女人既變態佬咁，<br />\n<br />\n捉住佢，<br />\n<br />\n驚唔小心用錯不適當武力既，<br />\n<br />\n擋，或者包圍。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔可以襲讓任人打成為風土病！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n【任務欄】<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1306215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1306215</a><br />\n任務眾多，請自行因應人數及背後目的考慮做邊D任 ；黃色為主線任務；紅色係Boss <br />\n7.11 - 梁烈士公眾告別禮 - <a href=\"http://t.me/leung711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fleung711&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt8520cGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=810467ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/leung711</a><br />\n7.11 - 油尖旺區議會夢遊 - <a href=\"http://t.me/ytm_dc711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fytm_dc711&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt8520cGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=413cdcef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/ytm_dc711</a><br />\n7.12 - 6.12一周月行動 - <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hklsd/photos/a.101378395784/10156221199385785/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhklsd%2Fphotos%2Fa.101378395784%2F10